'''始太古代'''（Eoarchean），是[[太古宙|太古宙]]第一个[[地质年代|代]]，也是地球形成固态地壳后首先有[[地质记录|地质记录]]的年代。它自40亿年前[[冥古宙|冥古宙]]结束后持续了4亿年，到36亿年前结束。地球的[[生命起源|生命起源]]大致在这一时期，[[蓝菌门|蓝菌门]]生物明确生存的时间可追溯至35亿年前。这时[[地球大气层|地球大气层]]中几乎没有氧，气压约在10到100[[巴|巴]]之间（现代的10到100分之一）。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Mulkidjanian |first=A. Y. | year=2009 | title=On the origin of life in the zinc world: 1. Photosynthesizing, porous edifices built of hydrothermally precipitated zinc sulfide as cradles of life on Earth. ll|journal=Biol. Direct |volume=4 |doi=10.1186/1745-6150-4-26|pmid=19703272 |pmc=3152778 }}</ref>{{rp|26}}<ref>{{cite journal | last=Mulkidjanian |first=A. Y. |author2=Bychkov, A. Y. |author3=Dibrova, D. V. |author4=Galperin, M. Y. |author5= Koonin, E. V. | year=2012 | title=Origin of first cells at terrestrial, anoxic geothermal fields |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA|doi=10.1073/pnas.1117774109 |bibcode = 2012PNAS..109E.821M | pmid=22331915 | pmc=3325685 | volume=109 | issue=14 |doi-access=free }}</ref>{{rp|E821–30}}<ref>{{cite encyclopedia | last=Mulkidjanian |first=A. Y. |year=2011 |title=Energetics of the First Life | encyclopedia=Origins of Life: The Primal Self-Organization|editor1-last=Egel|editor1-first=R.|editor2-last=Lankenau |editor2-first= D.-H. |editor3-first=A. Y.|editor3-last= Mulkidjanian |publisher= Springer Verlag|location= Heidelberg|isbn=978-3-642-21625-1}}</ref>{{rp|3–33}}

[[File:Greenlandite_(fuchsite-quartz_gneiss),_Greenland.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Garnet_paragneiss_Nuvvuagittuq_Greenstone_Belt,_4.28_Ga.jpg|thumb]]，加拿大Nuvvuagittuq绿岩带中，為地球已知最老的岩石（42.8亿年）。]]

==年代顺序==

始太古代最早被非正式地称为“早太古代”（已弃用）。<ref>{{cite web |title=Eoarchean Era |url=http://www.geologypage.com/2014/01/eoarchean-era.html |website=geologypage.com |date=16 January 2014 |access-date=2021-11-05 |archive-date=2021-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211108184713/https://www.geologypage.com/2014/01/eoarchean-era.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[国际地层委员会|国际地层委员会]]现在认证始太古代是[[太古宙|太古宙]]的第一部分，这一时期地球刚从熔融的状态冷却下来。<!-- In [[chronostratigraphy|chronostratigraphy]], its zone rank is an [[erathem|erathem]]. -->

始太古代下界或起点被[[国际地层委员会|国际地层委员会]]定义为40亿年前。<ref name="ICS2013">{{cite web | url=http://www.stratigraphy.org/ICSchart/ChronostratChart2013-01.pdf | title=International Chronostratigraphic Chart v.2013/01 | publisher=[[国际地层委员会|国际地层委员会]] | date=January 2013 | access-date=April 6, 2013 | archive-date=2013-09-01 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JJbYOJ8e?url=http://www.stratigraphy.org/ICSchart/ChronostratChart2013-01.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[瓦巴拉大陆|瓦巴拉大陆]]在始太古代末约36亿年前出现。

==地质==

在始太古代，地球首次形成固态[[地壳|地壳]]，不过并不完全，在其表面可能仍存在岩浆。始太古代的开端由内太阳系一次重大小行星撞击事件标记：即[[后期重轰炸期|后期重轰炸期]]。始太古代规模最大的成岩是格陵兰西南岸的[[伊苏阿绿岩带|伊苏阿绿岩带]]，它在38亿年前开始形成。[[加拿大地盾|加拿大地盾]]的[[阿卡斯塔片麻岩|阿卡斯塔片麻岩]]年代约为4031 Ma，是现存最古老的成岩。在2008年，[[魁北克|魁北克]]北部的Nuvvuagittuq绿岩带发现了年代约为4280Ma的成岩。<ref>{{cite journal | last=O'Neil | first=J. |author2=Carlson, R. W. |author3=Francis |author4=D. |author5= Stevenson, R. K.  |year=2008 | title=Neodymium-142 Evidence for Hadean Mafic Crust | journal=Science | volume=321 | issue=5897 | doi=10.1126/science.1161925 | pmid=18818357|bibcode = 2008Sci...321.1828O | s2cid=206514655 }}</ref>{{rp|1828–1831}}These formations are presently under intense investigation.{{clarify|date=June 2021}}<ref>{{cite journal|last1=David|first1=J.|last2=Godin|first2=L.|last3=Stevenson|first3=R. K.|last4=O'Neil|first4=J.|last5=Francis|first5=D.|title=U-Pb ages (3.8–2.7 Ga) and Nd isotope data from the newly identified Eoarchean Nuvvuagittuq supracrustal belt, Superior Craton, Canada|journal=Geological Society of America Bulletin|date=2009|volume=121|issue=1–2|doi=10.1130/B26369.1}}</ref>{{rp|150–163}}

==大气==
38.5亿年前的格陵兰[[磷灰石|磷灰石]]显示[[碳12|碳12]]浓度增加。这使得人们怀疑38亿年之前是否有光合作用生物存在。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Mojzsis|first1=S. J.|last2=Arrhenius|first2=G.|last3=McKeegan|first3=K. D.|last4=Harrison|first4=T. M.|last5=Nutman|first5=A. P.|last6=Friend|first6=C. R. L.|title=Evidence for life on Earth before 3,800 million years ago|url=https://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19980037618.pdf|journal=Nature|date=1996|volume=384|issue=6604|pages=55–59|doi=10.1038/384055a0|pmid=8900275|bibcode=1996Natur.384...55M|hdl=2060/19980037618|s2cid=4342620|hdl-access=free|access-date=2021-11-05|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105054612/https://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19980037618.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Update inline|reason=Debate was started at least 25 years ago - has it been resolved?|?=yes|date=September 2021}}

